Hey, Stimi-lust, get a grip there is now a lady present.  <br>
She wants a ride on your chopper, she thought it was a harley, civilians you know. <br><br>
Wants to know if you can still fly it. she wants to load it full of Vietnam style out door shitters and drop them on Clinton and Jiang during their summit talks. Figures that will get them to talk on some serious matters. She's a tough lady, put on lipstick and splashed on insect repellent just for the occasion. Likes to eat ham and Lima beans for breakfast. <br><br>
Thinks that anyone who can't hump two small, tiny, little dead does up a small ant hill shouldn't be hunting deer without a medivac chopper standing close by. Next time take SW with you, at least he'll be able to following the blood trails without getting sick. Should have called me, we could have used the M60, you wouldn't have had to travel six miles to find the tiny, little, lame, crippled, blind, two legged deer that you shot in the left ear. Good thing you had your P-38 with you, otherwise they would have gotten away.<br><br>
Chesty Puller said, You ain’t a Marine until you’ve done time in the brig. We used to pick on the Green Berets at the Thung Duc special Forces Camp just for tradition. Don’t know if stimulus – response had anything tot do with it, we just did it for fun. <br><br>

